<cb:div type="cbeta-notes">
<head>CBETA 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0554b06" resp="#resp3" type="mod_biao" target="#nkr_note_mod_biao_0554b06">言必能福彼非徒拔其貧苦而<choice cb:resp="#resp2"><corr>已</corr><sic>巳</sic></choice>故名不空食人之施</note>
<note n="0556b10" resp="#resp3" type="mod_biao" target="#nkr_note_mod_biao_0556b10">王士聞謂汝不達邪居士聞則謂佛實有疾何名為法之良醫身疾了能救而欲救人心疾乎夫法身虗假妙絕常境情累不能染心想不能議故曰諸漏<choice cb:resp="#resp2"><corr>已</corr><sic>己</sic></choice>盡過于三界之有漏</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div type="xuzang-notes">
<head>卍續藏 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0553b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0553b09">舍利弗於弟子中智慧第一故先論之</note>
<note n="0553b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0553b10">法身宴坐形神俱滅道絕常境視聽所不及豈復現身三界修意為定哉</note>
<note n="0553b11" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0553b11">上云不以三界現身意此云現諸威儀惟無現故能無不現無不現即無現之體</note>
<note n="0553b12" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0553b12">煩惱即涅槃故不待斷而後入也</note>
<note n="0553b13" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0553b13">目連名拘律陀樹神名也有大智慧神足第一者也</note>
<note n="0553b14" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0553b14">以下辯真法義眾生習著偏重故先言其無則垢自離</note>
<note n="0553b15" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0553b15">始終生死離則壽命無離者空之別名</note>
<note n="0554b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0554b01">有無非中於實為邊言有不有言無不無雖諸邊塵起不能轉之令異故言諸邊不動</note>
<note n="0554b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0554b02">迦葉以貧人昔不植福故生貧里若今不積善後復彌甚愍其長苦多就乞食淨名以其捨富從貧譏其不普即食之實相應以此心乞食</note>
<note n="0554b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0554b03">不受涅槃法也應以無受心而受彼食是終日受而未甞受也</note>
<note n="0554b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0554b04">八邪八解本性常一善觀八邪即入八解曷為舍邪更求解脫乎</note>
<note n="0554b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0554b05">小乘入定則不食食則不入定法身大士終日食而終日定故無出入名</note>
<note n="0554b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0554b06">言必能福彼非徒拔其貧苦而巳故名不空食人之施</note>
<note n="0554b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0554b07">取鉢盛飯未授之間譏其不等也</note>
<note n="0554b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0554b08">恃定而來於定為不等矣即以食詰之者明于食亦不等也豈等定哉</note>
<note n="0554b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0554b09">天地齊旨萬物一觀邪正雖殊其性不二豈有如來獨尊六師獨卑乎若能同彼六師不見佛不聞法因其出家隨其所墮而不為異乃可取食</note>
<note n="0554b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0554b10">既為其侶安得有異夫以無異故能成其異</note>
<note n="0554b11" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0554b11">等觀者以存善為患故舍善求宗以捨惡為累故即惡反本則同善未為得同惡未為失淨名言意似在此乎</note>
<note n="0554b12" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0554b12">弟子中解空第一既知化之無心亦知法之復如化聽之何懼</note>
<note n="0554b13" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0554b13">解脫謂無為真解脫也名生于不足足則無名故無文字</note>
<note n="0555b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0555b01">迎毗耶離城有園林僧房富樓那于中為新學說法</note>
<note n="0555b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0555b02">穢食充饑小乘法也盛無上寶大乘器也</note>
<note n="0555b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0555b03">四喻戒之說法錯落精奇珠璣滿楮</note>
<note n="0555b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0555b04">淨名將開其宿心成其本意令諸比丘暫識宿命自知會于五百佛所植眾德本也向無上道此其本也</note>
<note n="0555b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0555b05">摩訶迦旃延南天竺婆羅門姓也善解契經</note>
<note n="0555b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0555b06">如來言說未常有心其所說法未常有想迦旃延不喻玄旨入室皆以相說故淨名破其互相此言同旨異迦旃延致惑也</note>
<note n="0555b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0555b07">小乘以三界熾然故滅之以求無為夫熾然既形故滅名以生大乘觀法本自不然今何所滅不然不滅乃真寂滅也</note>
<note n="0555b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0555b08">阿那律如意也剎利種弟子中天眼第一</note>
<note n="0555b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0555b09">梵王聞阿那律天眼第一故問所見遠近</note>
<note n="0555b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0555b10">色無色相若有遠近精麤即是為色作相而進退無可</note>
<note n="0555b11" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0555b11">若不以色作相是真天眼未知誰有故問言孰也</note>
<note n="0555b12" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0555b12">二乘在定則見出定不見如來未甞不見未甞不定故常在三昧</note>
<note n="0555b13" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0555b13">優波離長存願誓世世常作持律故于今持律第一</note>
<note n="0555b14" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0555b14">愧其所犯不敢問佛以優波離持律故悔其既往廢亂道行請特律解免斯咎</note>
<note n="0555b15" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0555b15">以罪為罪則心生垢累不以罪為罪此即淨心即眾生淨也</note>
<note n="0555b16" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0555b16">萬法云々皆由心起豈獨垢淨然哉諸不離于如如謂如本相也</note>
<note n="0556b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0556b01">奉律一名毗尼又名善治謂自治謠悲（謠悲恐淫恚）痴亦能治眾生惡也</note>
<note n="0556b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0556b02">羅睺羅一名阿修羅即覆障也謂障月明也稱密行第一</note>
<note n="0556b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0556b03">世榮雖樂難可久保出家之理長樂無為</note>
<note n="0556b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0556b04">偽出家者惡此生死尊彼涅槃故有中間三處之異真出家者遺萬累亡彼此豈有此三處哉</note>
<note n="0556b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0556b05">無所受欲受我受戒受見受四受也</note>
<note n="0556b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0556b06">出家本欲離惡行道若在家而能發意即具足矣</note>
<note n="0556b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0556b07">阿難即名歡喜也弟子之中總持第一</note>
<note n="0556b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0556b08">小乘骨金剛肉非金剛也</note>
<note n="0556b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0556b09">大乘內外金剛一切實滿有大勢力無病處故</note>
<note n="0556b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0556b10">王士聞謂汝不達邪居士聞則謂佛實有疾何名為法之良醫身疾了能救而欲救人心疾乎夫法身虗假妙絕常境情累不能染心想不能議故曰諸漏己盡過于三界之有漏</note>
<note n="0556b11" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0556b11">五濁劫濁眾生濁煩惱濁見濁命濁多歲數名由泓多由泓名為劫</note>
</p>
